---
layout: base.liquid
title: Spencer Mills Orthodox Presbyterian Church
description: Spencer Mills is a vibrant, confessionally Reformed church in Gowen, MI that seeks to make disciples of Jesus Christ who worship God with great joy.
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img src="/assets/images/SpencerMIlls_Sanctuary.jpg" alt="Spencer Mills Sanctuary" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy/40"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white mb-4">Worship at Spencer Mills</h1>
    <p class="font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl text-light-green italic mb-6">Glorifying and Enjoying God Together.</p>
    <p class="text-white/90 text-lg mb-8">Please join us for Sunday services at {{ site.services.morning }} and {{ site.services.evening }}.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="#location" class="inline-block bg-white border-2 border-white text-navy px-8 py-3 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors">
        Join Us
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@SpencerMillsChurch/streams" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
        Live Stream
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Welcome Section -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-off-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-navy text-center mb-8">Welcome to Spencer Mills Orthodox Presbyterian Church</h2>
    <p class="text-navy/80 text-center leading-relaxed">
      Spencer Mills is a vibrant, confessionally Reformed church that seeks to make disciples of Jesus Christ who worship God with great joy, walk alongside one another in Christian love, and seek to share the good news of the gospel of Jesus Christ with those around us near and far. At Spencer Mills you will hear God's Word preached each and every Sunday and be comforted by the peace we have with God in Jesus Christ.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Divider -->
<div class="bg-off-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl">
    <hr class="border-t border-light-blue/50">
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Listen, Church Life & Calendar Section -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-off-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Column 1: Listen -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-navy mb-4">Listen</h2>
        <p class="text-navy/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Hear past sermons from our pastor and guest speakers in our Sermon Archive.
        </p>
        <a href="/sermons/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-spruce uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:underline transition-colors group">
          Sermons
          <span class="inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">‚Üí</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 2: Church Life -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-navy mb-4">Church Life</h2>
        <p class="text-navy/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Whether it's midweek classes, a hymn sing, or a fellowship meal, Spencer Mills has activities for members and visitors on a regular basis. We would love to have you join us!
        </p>
        <a href="/beliefs/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-spruce uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:underline transition-colors group">
          Our Beliefs
          <span class="inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">‚Üí</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 3: Calendar Widget -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm h-fit">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-navy mb-4">Upcoming Events</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-navy/60 mb-4">Next 7 days</p>

        {% if calendar.size > 0 %}
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            {% for event in calendar %}
            <li class="border-l-4 border-spruce pl-4">
              <h4 class="text-navy">{{ event.title }}</h4>
              <time class="text-sm text-navy/70 block mt-1">
                {{ event.formattedDateTime }}
              </time>
              {% if event.location %}
                <p class="text-sm text-navy/60 mt-1">üìç {{ event.location }}</p>
              {% endif %}
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% else %}
          <p class="text-navy/60 text-sm">No upcoming events in the next 7 days.</p>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
          <a href="https://outlook.office365.com/owa/calendar/7968b2c0fc1749959aa5c1ff78db8e87@lfcopc.org/68138daf3a834607ae3394f3497a07fa4237023610457132402/calendar.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-spruce text-sm hover:underline">View Full Calendar</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Location Section -->
<section id="location" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-navy mb-4">Our Location</h2>
    <p class="text-navy/80 mb-8">We meet at {{ site.address.street }}, {{ site.address.city }}, {{ site.address.state }} {{ site.address.zip }}.</p>

    <!-- Google Maps Embed -->
    <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm aspect-video">
      <iframe
        src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=12710+17+Mile+Rd+NE,+Gowen,+MI+49326&t=&z=11&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed"
        width="100%"
        height="100%"
        style="border:0"
        allowfullscreen=""
        loading="lazy"
        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
        title="Spencer Mills Orthodox Presbyterian Church Location"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact Section -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-navy">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-2xl">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-white mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 mb-8">
      Can we be of assistance to you in some way? We would love the chance to get to know you. Please fill out the form below and we'll be in touch. Thanks!
    </p>

    <!-- Contact Form -->
    <form class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label for="name" class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70 mb-1">Name*</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="enter your name" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-white/30 rounded bg-navy text-white placeholder-white/40 focus:outline-none focus:border-spruce transition-colors">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="email" class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70 mb-1">Email*</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="enter your email address" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-white/30 rounded bg-navy text-white placeholder-white/40 focus:outline-none focus:border-spruce transition-colors">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="subject" class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70 mb-1">Subject*</label>
        <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required placeholder="enter the subject of your message" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-white/30 rounded bg-navy text-white placeholder-white/40 focus:outline-none focus:border-spruce transition-colors">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="message" class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70 mb-1">Message</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" placeholder="how can we help?" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-white/30 rounded bg-navy text-white placeholder-white/40 focus:outline-none focus:border-spruce transition-colors resize-y"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center pt-4">
        <button type="submit" class="bg-spruce text-white px-10 py-3 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-spruce/90 transition-colors">
          Submit
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
